item.title: WORKSHOP 2016
item.description:
WORKSHOP 2016 

Based on the previous press-release and an increasing demand from the public we are happy to announce Verkstedet-method / Pimp My Body has scheduled two Workshops, 16th of January or 13th of February, where we will present the verkstedet-method. The workshops will inform you "know the path" about the "Verkstedet-method". If you would like to try it out yourself,  "walk the path", workshop participants have discount.
